; UTILITY: lopass gate — Buchla-style, one control opens amplitude and brightness together.
; `ping` strikes it (a trigger), `decay` sets the pluck length. The gate closes between pings,
; so it is silent at rest (for a sustained drone, open the lpg with a held CV instead).
(def lopass-gate (fn (:in :ping :decay)
  (lpg in (envelope :trig ping :decay decay))))
